            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>drained penne</strong> and the <strong>baby leaf spinach</strong> to the <strong>tomato sauce</strong> with 100ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[150ml] </span>of the<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span><strong>starchy pasta water</strong></p>\n<p>Mix it all together and cook for 2-3 min or until the <strong>spinach</strong> is wilted and everything is coated in the sauce</p>",
